latestIgtvVideos.title: BEGINNERS GLAM TUTORIAL❤️
Purple Glitter Eyes💜
Date Night Get Ready With Me!
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Before putting on makeup for a date night, skin prep is so important! Scrubbing and masking definitely helps. I used few products from @pulp_india which is a clean, vegan and cruelty free brand😍
The ‘Coffee and Love’ scrub gently exfoliates the skin without being too harsh. It is packed with Açai, Coffee and Coco beans and smells delicious. 
The ‘Date Night Prep’ mask is a super food mask with a combo of Kombucha and Rose. My skin felt soft and smooth after using it. 
The combination of these two products definitely made my skin ready for flawless makeup💕
@pulp_india @pulpxx 
#bffcertified #pulpindia
